<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="on-the-condition-that">on (the) condition that</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>在…条件下；倘若：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They agreed to lend us the car on condition that we returned it before the weekend. 
他们同意把车借给我们，条件是我们必须在周末前归还。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I would consider studying abroad, on the condition that I get a scholarship. 
倘若获得奖学金，我会考虑出国学习。</p></div></div>